# Cursor Rules Directory

This directory contains Cursor AI rules files (.mdc format).

Cursor automatically reads all .mdc files in this directory in alphabetical order.

## File Organization

- `00-overview.mdc` - Project overview and critical rules
- `01-project-structure.mdc` - Project structure conventions
- `02-go-zero-conventions.mdc` - Go-Zero framework conventions
- `03-code-style.mdc` - Code style and best practices
- `04-architecture.mdc` - Architecture rules
- `05-requirements.mdc` - Testing, documentation, and security requirements
- `06-development-workflow.mdc` - Development workflow (TDD)
- `07-code-review.mdc` - Code review requirements
- `08-git-workflow.mdc` - Git workflow and commit standards
- `09-code-explanation.mdc` - Code explanation standards (design purpose, git history, module relationships, global role)
